field generator.<br>
2. The star wars tech manuel that some fans are familiar<br>
with does not  apply the laws of physics to anything it says,<br>
and it therefore can not be canon for star wars technologies.<br>
3. The fusion main sequance:<br>
In nature all natural elements including all the heavy ones can be produced by nuclear fusion during the life cycle of the stars. They can also undergo nuclear fusion to build still heavier natural elements. <br>
Here is the fusion main sequance briefly described:<br>
p + p + p +p = he3  + 0n1 + energy +  neutrino<br>
Then he3 + he3 + he 3 + he3  = carbon 12<br>
Then the carbons fuse to form heavier elements such as<br>
